Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "Saquero@pruebas.com",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

### Get users paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get subscription plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription-plans

### Assign Basic plan to user 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Subscriptions/assign/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": 1,
  "endDate": "2026-05-01"
}

### Get active subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Subscriptions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter active subscriptions by plan
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Subscriptions/active?planId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get subscriptions expiring soon
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Subscriptions/expiring-soon?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel subscription
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/Subscriptions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
